/></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/225345_f019ca1f5b20b2ccac21210880b50160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F225345_f019ca1f5b20b2ccac21210880b50160.jpg&h=46c18637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我極度推薦呢本導讀，睇完之後真係個人看待世界嘅睇法完全唔同晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係書局見過，有機會買黎睇"},{"pid":"b3e4e5f3bd8312ea18f1fc101b3d56245773fa70","tid":5965,"uid":28866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"對形上學有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無書係主力講下啲哲學家對呢個範疇既見解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.s. 對哲學得好少認知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日係到諗時間,空間,存在究竟係乜"},{"pid":"fd3341c9d2150ca8fc0ec6cbb41fef1400f48789","tid":5965,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對形上學有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無書係主力講下啲哲學家對呢個範疇既見解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.s. 對哲學得好少認知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日係到諗時間,空間,存在究竟係乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老子、莊子之天道為形上天<br />\n推薦《老莊新論》陳鼓應<br />\n<br />\n墨子天志為人格天<br />\n<br />\n孔孟之天命為有一客觀限制之命定，但命中顯義，即有分人所能/不能主宰之領域<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打對中國思想哲學有興趣，可以討論下。另推薦勞思光先生《新編中國哲學史》，獨創基源問題研究法作全面性全面性判斷。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，史係陳述歷史事實既意思，但哲學史除左係史之外，有一極為重要既元素就係哲學。胡適之先生本中國哲學史除左係未完成之作之外，仲有一致命問題，就係不含哲學部分。"},{"pid":"f0068485d0a3d0a1284feaf59cb060895defece4","tid":5965,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對形上學有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無書係主力講下啲哲學家對呢個範疇既見解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.s. 對哲學得好少認知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日係到諗時間,空間,存在究竟係乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入門有Riddles of existence"},{"pid":"97f1d3abb9a6d948c84eeeccf7e78d8579c422a2","tid":5965,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩開始接觸哲學 <br />\n有無話睇邊幾本書入門？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主有開另一個post介紹入門書 好多都好岩初學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過如果你本身冇任何文科底我建議睇啲最淺既入門書<br />\nMichael Sandel - Justice<br />\n或者果啲咩一本通曉果啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJustice 係唔錯<br />\n通曉嗰啲我唔敢保證質素<br />\nBtw我高中都係讀science <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56ea8f849718fd04e2b91df6dd8810271eb12c3","tid":5965,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主喜好咩哲學？ 分析，歐陸，中國？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英美（分析）<br />\n一來我讀理科<br />\n二來我當初聽到分析呢個名已經覺得好型<br />\n至於中國，有接觸過啲"},{"pid":"22471ee7014b558068b2865fc56cffeee07d4f21","tid":5965,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名，近排睇左卡繆本異鄉人，覺得呢個世界跟本就係piece of shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享下本書大概想表達咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n卡繆寫中好多中二病毒撚心聲<br />\n但佢自己係高大靚仔做運動，<br />\n十幾個女朋友，識著衫，係社會上流人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗起呂大樂寫四代香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔明佢想表達咩，我道行未夠高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <